}# sporting-goods-store-vite

This is a minimal Vite + React demo store for *Apex Sporting Goods* (no backend, demo only).

## Features
- React front-end with search + product cards
- Ready to connect to payments (Stripe) and supplier API
- Deploy to Vercel or Netlify

## Run locally
1. Install Node.js (>=16)
2. npm install
3. npm run dev
4. Open the printed local URL (usually http://localhost:5173)

## Deploy to Vercel
1. Push this repo to GitHub
2. Sign in to Vercel and import the repository
3. Vercel will detect Viimport React from 'react'
